VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'hit over 14,000 stars on GitHub in weeks. And a lot of devs have been talking about it. In the next minute, I\'ll show you how this works and how it\'s going to immensely speed up your understanding of your code base.'

[00:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Understand anything is an open-source Claude code plugin. It can also fit into workflows with tools like Cursor, Copilot, and Gemini CLI. You point it at'

